public abstract class AbstractAppPlugin
extends AbstractPlugin

AbstractAppPlugin is an abstract base class for Plugins basing on the hierarchy of the site to perform a test. Each URL under the selected node will be traversed and launch a plugin to test. Multiple threads will be executed. But AbstractAppPlugin must complete before another can start.
